  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_828672\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_2491299_828672\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481828\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_2491299_481828\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Distance Learning</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6756584\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/education/learning/images/Green-Screen-Bison.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Park Ranger makes bison horns with their fingers in front of an aspen backdrop with bison in the field.\" src=\"/grca/learn/education/learning/images/Green-Screen-Bison.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Distance Learning Green Screen Bison\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption><p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p><strong>Grand Canyon National Park offers free state-of-the-art distance learning programs, primarily for Title I schools in Arizona, New Mexico, Utah, Colorado, southern Nevada, and California near the Arizona border. Programs are conducted via videoconferencing platforms, such as Zoom, Webex, Google Meet, etc.</strong></p>\n<h2>Program Schedule and Registration:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Registration for the 2024-2025 school year is currently <strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">CLOSED</span></strong>. </li>\n<li>For activities to facilitate in your classroom, check out <a href=\"https://www.grandcanyon.org/classes-tours/youth-programs/cfs-home/\" id=\"https://www.grandcanyon.org/classes-tours/youth-programs/cfs-home/|\">Canyon Field School @Home</a> and <a href=\"/grca/learn/education/student-report-information.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6777956,student-report-information.htm,14078|\">Student Report Information</a>. </li>\n<li>Other on-demand videos that immerse students in the Grand Canyon include <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715|\">Rim Walk of Grand Canyon Village</a>, the <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/minute-out-in-it.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2349686,minute-out-in-it.htm,14075|\">Minute Out In It</a> Series, and the park's <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/webcams.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1927865,webcams.htm,14075|\">live webcams</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>If your class meets the criteria above, and you have questions about the program, please</strong> <a href=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4C97D8BA99DABCA895B510AAF512AABF489448887CB89C8C1118A191&amp;r=/grca/learn/education/learning/index.htm\" id=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=4C97D8BA99DABCA895B510AAF512AABF489448887CB89C8C1118A191&amp;r=/grca/learn/education/learning/index.htm|\">e-mail us</a><b>.</b></h4>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7893554\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7893554\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-9DA2AFA3-CFC8-6981-1F774F8769DF12B3\">\n<h2>On-Demand Programs- Watch On Your Own Schedule!</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-9DA2AFA3-CFC8-6981-1F774F8769DF12B3\">Narrow By Location:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-facet-Organizations_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Organizations_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Office\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-organizations\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-9DA2AFA3-CFC8-6981-1F774F8769DF12B3\">Narrow By Office:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-count-select\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"sort-by\" id=\"result-count-form\"><p><label for=\"result-count-select-searchListing-9DA2AFA3-CFC8-6981-1F774F8769DF12B3\">Show</label><select id=\"result-count-select-searchListing-9DA2AFA3-CFC8-6981-1F774F8769DF12B3\" name=\"result-maxRows\">\n<option value=\"10\">10</option>\n<option value=\"40\">40</option>\n</select></p></form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><!--display-list-view-->\n<div class=\"FilterTags\" style=\"display:none;\"></div>\n<div class=\"ListingResults-loading\">\nLoading results...\n</div>\n<ul class=\"resultsUL\"></ul>\n</div><!--results-->\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n<div class=\"resultsPaginationArea\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7895936\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7895936\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h3>On Demand Video:</h3>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7893586\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7893586\"> \n\n<div class=\"gallery-listing-av webcam-gallery responsiveVideoLinkNoHighlights\">\n<ul class=\"gallery-content-av clearfix\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"image\">\n<a class=\"cc\" href=\"/media/video/view.htm?id=C81DB998-9A6F-416C-BB11-968D31E4E7B4\">\n<div style=\"background: url('/common/uploads/imr/park/grca//2173823D-DB74-6BB6-14AC0FEF1898BC7F/2173823D-DB74-6BB6-14AC0FEF1898BC7F-thumbnail.png') center center black;\">\n<img alt=\"Exploring Geology at Grand Canyon National Park\" border=\"0\" class=\"avArea-thumb\" src=\"/common/commonspot/templates/images/buttons/thumb_play_button.png\"/>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-9 col-sm-9 col-xs-12 avItem\">\n<div class=\"avDescription clearfix\">\n<h3><a class=\"cc\" href=\"/media/video/view.htm?id=C81DB998-9A6F-416C-BB11-968D31E4E7B4\">Exploring Geology at Grand Canyon National Park</a></h3>\n<p>Join rangers in this engaging journey through Grand Canyon National Park, where we uncover the geological wonders and cultural significance of this breathtaking landscape! From the South Rim to the North Rim and the depths of the canyon, discover how the canyon was formed and how it continues to change.</p>\n<dl class=\"result-details wrapped\">\n<dt>Duration:</dt><dd>24 minutes, 46 seconds</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7895937\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7895937\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6756618\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6756618\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-9DA2C22B-CE12-2F09-802402964FEAA341\">\n<h2>Live Ranger Programs</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-s